HEADWORD: Dovish
<hw>Dov"ish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Like a
dove; harmless; innocent.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Joined with <xex>dovish</xex>
simplicity.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Latimer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
